Developer Terms of Use
des:
Presented by Dave Rush, a 20 year EMT with Highland Rescue in Golden Colorado, Denver Health tips was created to remind listeners of of good health practices as well as tips from an expert. We will cover everything from ways to avoid the cold and flu to how to recognize when someone is having a heart attack! 

The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only.
